I AM UGLY

Holla everyone. 
Don't you know, that usually people who call themselves ugly actually wanna get called the opposite?
Well, I'm not one of them.
Here's the statement: I'm ugly.
I spent 40 minutes staring while drawing my own face, and this picture is myself with a lot of modification, so, you know, the real me might be worse.
Thank you for still looking at this post, thanks.
Ps. I've been re-reading slam dunk manga for a whole day, so it affected my shading technique.
